      "date": "2015-02-05 23:42:12.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThis does work BTW.\n\n \nq:lustre# echo XXX > f0\nq:lustre# lfs hsm_archive f0\nq:lustre# lfs hsm_release f0\nq:lustre# stat f0\n  File: `f0'\n  Size: 4         \tBlocks: 1          IO Block: 4194304 regular file\nDevice: 2c54f966h/743766374d\tInode: 144115205255725057  Links: 1\nAccess: (0644/-rw-r--r--)  Uid: (    0/    root)   Gid: (    0/    root)\nAccess: 2015-02-05 17:33:57.000000000 -0600\nModify: 2015-02-05 17:33:58.000000000 -0600\nChange: 2015-02-05 17:33:58.000000000 -0600\nq:lustre# lfs hsm_restore f0\nq:lustre# stat f0\n  File: `f0'\n  Size: 4         \tBlocks: 8          IO Block: 4194304 regular file\nDevice: 2c54f966h/743766374d\tInode: 144115205255725057  Links: 1\nAccess: (0644/-rw-r--r--)  Uid: (    0/    root)   Gid: (    0/    root)\nAccess: 2015-02-05 17:33:57.000000000 -0600\nModify: 2015-02-05 17:33:58.000000000 -0600\nChange: 2015-02-05 17:33:58.000000000 -0600\nq:lustre# \nq:lustre# \nq:lustre# lfs hsm_release f0\nq:lustre# tar -cf /tmp/f0.tar f0\nq:lustre#",
